How Our Program Works

Break Free from Debt Your Financial Freedom Starts Now

At DCG, our experienced attorneys take care of the entire MCA debt restructuring process, giving you the freedom to focus on what matters most: running and growing your business. We handle the negotiations with your lenders to secure better termsso you can move forward with confidence and clarity.

STEP 1
Get a Free Consultation

Connect with one of DCGs MCA specialists for a complimentary, no-obligation consultation. Well assess your unique financial situation and determine whether our program is the right fit for you.

STEP 2
Attorney Review of Terms

Our skilled legal team will carefully examine the terms and conditions of your MCA agreement(s) to uncover opportunities for restructuring and to prepare a strong negotiation strategy.

STEP 3
Negotiate Improved Terms

With a thorough understanding of your MCA contract, our attorneys will engage with your lender(s) to negotiate more favorable termssuch as reduced payments, longer repayment periods, lower fees, and enhanced cash flow.

STEP 4
Finalize the New Agreement

After securing new terms, well oversee the finalization of your restructured agreement and guide you through a seamless transition into a more manageable repayment plan.
